PXP000JB.text:
)ATTR DEFAULT(¢$_)
)body
¢TUTORIAL -------------- PANEXEC LIBRARY MAINTENANCE - BACKUP --------- TUTORIAL
¢OPTION  ===>_ZCMD                                                             $
$                                                                              $
      The JCL generated by the BACKUP option is as follows:                    $
//jobname JOB                                                                  $
//STEP1 EXEC PGM=PANEXEC,REGION=1024K,PARM='%INPUT PXSTBKUP/;T'                $
//*      RUN EASYTRIEVE REPORTS AND BKUP PANEXEC LIBRARY                       $
//*          REPORTS PE101,PE117,PE106,PE108,PE110,PE107                       $
//STEPLIB  DD DSN=HRA.PANESRL,DISP=SHR                                         $
